{"tid":816714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國自主研發頹爆動物園　網民：有動物看還想怎樣…","createTime":"2018-09-13T02:17:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T15:33:50.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"08ffeaf80eac09c07ab19c05138cb9a3dd43f652","tid":816714,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T02:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1751592/org/d08c2ff963b35d12859719de1047f570.png/IVcYLdooU2AKSVOyU0oHBLASWflL0gWujvMUc47zFHM?v=w1600r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1751592%2Forg%2Fd08c2ff963b35d12859719de1047f570.png%2FIVcYLdooU2AKSVOyU0oHBLASWflL0gWujvMUc47zFHM%3Fv%3Dw1600r16_9&h=0b0a0347&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n山寨文化在中國社會上可說是屢見不鮮，但此文化經已延伸至動物園裡你又會否相信？日前一間中國網上媒體派記者到訪了華北其中一個動物園，並發現園內動物的樣子大多是沒神采，最令人疑惑的是，園內還有很多奇怪的設施及表演項目，不少網民看了短片均表示：「這真是我一輩子見過最頹廢的動物園」。<br />\n<br />\n內地一名記者日前到華北一間動物園參觀，從短片裡顯示，動物園的入口設施已顯示出其「頹爆」文化，園外的售票處設施亦相當簡陋，入口附近還有一些小販正在售賣玩具，若非仔細觀察，平常人根本無法得悉這是一間動物園。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1751618/org/eacb2821900baed89c3c0ec9606aa3c8.png/nw5T4JSkDpq6q6rzkZHbpaLoFFDvJ-zZT3v3lk9795Y?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1751618%2Forg%2Feacb2821900baed89c3c0ec9606aa3c8.png%2Fnw5T4JSkDpq6q6rzkZHbpaLoFFDvJ-zZT3v3lk9795Y%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=f89f65f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當記者進入到園內，已發現全部動物並不是一些特別的品種，基本上全部動物皆可在外面的動物商店中購買，「虎皮鸚鵡和你家裡養的也差不多。」記者嘲諷說道。動物園內連普通的鬥牛㹴亦是展示動物之一，動物園亦為牠改了一個特別的名字「比特犬」，嘗試給遊客一種錯覺是，這隻狗是一隻罕有、時尚的狗狗。記者走了動物園一圈亦發現，全部動物在籠子裡全部也是沒神采的，與其他動物園的動物比較，實在沒那麼活潑，從短片已經可以感受到，整個動物園所散發出的「頹態」是非常強烈的。<br />\n<br />\n不過最令記者感到大惑不解的是，動物園裡還有大大少少令人感到突兀的設施和表演項目。記者在參觀動物園途中走到了一個位置，突然看到眼前有一個奇怪的遊覽設施「哥德號鬼船」，裡面所呈現的擺設及展品亦令人摸不著頭腦，有網民在短片留言：「天呀！這究竟是甚麼動物園來的，園內怎麼會有鬼屋的存在&hellip;」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1751599/org/e44e5c28d713e30e47518d77cff3b9ed.png/PyhKayCAjzYMKc4NW8JatcTkR-pZ0bR4y9gWVMvYFlQ?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1751599%2Forg%2Fe44e5c28d713e30e47518d77cff3b9ed.png%2FPyhKayCAjzYMKc4NW8JatcTkR-pZ0bR4y9gWVMvYFlQ%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=f5278e15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記者玩完鬼屋後甫出「鬼門」，就發現眼前有一個標牌寫著「人蛇表演」，最令人哭笑不得的是記者進到表演場地，已發現一條大蟒蛇已在台上，很明顯地是園內的工作人員隨意放置大蛇在台上不作理會，隨後一位身穿紅衣的中年女士從後台走出，並播放著「大媽音樂」邀請記者共舞。不少網民看完這段短片後紛紛表示驚訝，並希望記者可以道出動物園的名字，笑說記者若不公開的話「將有更多烈士身亡」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%AF%B5%E7%89%A9/223023/%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87-%E8%8F%AF%E5%8C%97%E9%A0%B9%E7%88%86%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E5%9C%92-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E6%88%B2%E7%A8%B1-%E6%9C%89%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E7%9C%8B%E9%82%84%E6%83%B3%E6%80%8E%E6%A8%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%25AF%25B5%25E7%2589%25A9%2F223023%2F%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2589%2587-%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%258C%2597%25E9%25A0%25B9%25E7%2588%2586%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2589%25A9%25E5%259C%2592-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2588%25B2%25E7%25A8%25B1-%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2589%25A9%25E7%259C%258B%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%2583%25B3%25E6%2580%258E%25E6%25A8%25A3&d=qpIW4utTcIAj%2BOeL76mdrf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=a670d23e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%AF%B5%E7%89%A9/223023/%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87-%E8%8F%AF%E5%8C%97%E9%A0%B9%E7%88%86%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E5%9C%92-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E6%88%B2%E7%A8%B1-%E6%9C%89%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E7%9C%8B%E9%82%84%E6%83%B3%E6%80%8E%E6%A8%A3</a>"},{"pid":"45b00d713033bc3a5ecfdb0767b1d1f5f5008b6d","tid":816714,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T04:03:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1333ed19d80484427a13f94f7ffc18cce9016cfa","tid":816714,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T04:05:15.000Z","msg":"留名等睇扮動物笑話"},{"pid":"a46da6373aa33212334d3076532541605dbaa4f0","tid":816714,"uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T07:20:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/2141/8475/products/Hot_Toys_-_Christopher_Robin_-_Winnie_the_Pooh_Piglet_Collectible_Set_PR1_1024x.jpg?v=1535008726\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.shopify.com%2Fs%2Ffiles%2F1%2F2141%2F8475%2Fproducts%2FHot_Toys_-_Christopher_Robin_-_Winnie_the_Pooh_Piglet_Collectible_Set_PR1_1024x.jpg%3Fv%3D1535008726&h=e0a693a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fdf51fbf76e52e9e9865ea5191c044e857554d31","tid":816714,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T08:25:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c820a2ea3e1956387ee1643e32906d63100c781","tid":816714,"uid":130225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T08:34:30.000Z","msg":"比特犬有咩問題...."},{"pid":"07d401b9821ca2a87ab654ea31c752e88bbd4ca3","tid":816714,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T13:41:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a72d97e2851957a67993773c44d7afcbcad4962","tid":816714,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T15:33:50.000Z","msg":"又post紅1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}